node.text:
Being yourself is the most beautiful thing you can be 💕 I want to see what makes you, you! Post a photo that you feel shows your most authentic self and use #BeHue in the caption✨ I’ll be going through your posts and choosing 5 of you to win a bottle of my perfume 🥰 Make sure you go to the most recent post on @huefragrance for details on how you can win!! Love you!

PS While we are *still* working hard to make Hue available internationally, @cosmofragrances is able to extend this giveaway to fans in Canada, Western Europe, and the UK
